9
00:00:40,332 --> 00:00:42,501
<i>Datang semula setelah awak sembuh.</i>

10
00:00:43,461 --> 00:00:44,879
<i>Saya akan bunuh awak waktu itu.</i>

11
00:00:46,422 --> 00:00:47,506
Asirpa.

12
